International Business Machines Corporation (B)
David F. Hawkins
IBM changes pension plan from a defined benefit plan to a cash-balance plan. Teaching purpose: To understand pension accounting.
Keywords: Business or Company Management; 
				  Transformation; 
				  Business Earnings; 
				  Private Sector; 
				  Personal Finance; 
				  Cash; 
				  Hardware; 
				  Taxation; 
				  Computer Industry; 
				  Accounting Industry; 
				  

Citation:Hawkins, David F. "International Business Machines Corporation (B)." Harvard Business School Case 100-033, November 1999. (Revised April 2002.) View Details




